name: PLUTO
description: Pluto is a memecoin, representing the religion called Church Of Dulo. It's built on the Solana blockchain. The Pluto character is a delusional cat, who believes in himself and the crypot market to take him higher and higher. We are producing high quality art for our X account that other traders have greatly enjoyed so far. We plan on growing the cult of Pluto until everyone is as delusional as Pluto the cat.
